{"tid":622180,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你想見到既歐聯四強同決賽對戰組合","createTime":"2018-04-09T03:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T23:54:46.000Z","uid":5006,"like":56,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"04ef3862afd9d77b46d23545483b616f9b0edcb3","tid":622180,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>四強</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">利 vs 巴 </span><br />\n想睇紅軍大演進攻足球，睇下佢地大破曼城果套用唔用得返巴塞身上，想睇高普成為控球克星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，想睇埋蘇9倒戈，贏輸都應該好有睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實想睇埋古天樂條反骨失敗，可惜無機會<br />\n另外都想睇埃及美斯大戰真美斯，沙拿贏到就真係威威喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">皇 vs 拜</span><br />\n唔想又睇西甲打吡，唯有睇強強對話<br />\nC朗仲keep唔keep到態，過到保方再過埋紐亞果十指關（可惜曼聯出局，否則打埋迪基亞就最好）<br />\n究竟係拜仁復仇成功，定係再一次傷盡拜仁fans心？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>決賽</strong><br />\n雖然可能不大，但都想睇<span style=\"color: red;\"> 利 vs 皇</span><br />\n<br />\n想紅軍為英超爭光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦想睇兩隊決賽鬥攻踢熱血足球，咪成日泊大巴同控球最後踢到加時咁實睇到恰眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6f035aa9eff5bb992078922057a2c24a710025","tid":622180,"uid":136116,"like":58,"dislike":4,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"決賽曼聯vs皇馬<br />\n其他是撚但"},{"pid":"8ebe2664355c034b96dd04ab48744211aa43ceb4","tid":622180,"uid":128014,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"上面兩位已經講哂我心聲出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決賽想睇曼聯對利物浦<img src=\"/assets/fa